                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Mr. Abraham Hart</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">President of the Congregation “Mikveh Israel„</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <placeName>Pa</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written sideways to the left of the address\">Letter &amp;\n                Proceedings from the Congregation<lb/> K. K. B. E. <date>21st Tammus</date><lb/>\n                Also copy of reply <date>July 25. 1843</date>.<lb/> (<date>1843</date>)</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
